description:
Right here is where you will find the perfect foundation for your new forever home. Situated approximately 500m from the stunning shores of Geographe Bay and “oh so close” to the city centre, all desirable amenities are right at your fingertips.
Take advantage of the 18.5m frontage, 35m depth and neat rectangular shape by incorporating side access and a shed into your building design, which this family sized lot can certainly accommodate. Being positioned with a North facing orientation, also offers the perfect chance to create an outdoor entertaining area bathed in the morning and afternoon sunshine.
The location itself is close to parklands, local primary school, local and city shopping, Port Geographe Marina, restaurants and cafés and a variety of sporting facilities.
With a vast shortage of land prospects presently available, much less those located so close to the Busselton Foreshore, this truly is a magnificent buying opportunity that should not be passed up.
Contact me today Craig Davies on 0419 962 773 to make your property dreams come true.
